Package: siru
Version: 0.4.2
Section: web
Priority: optional
Architecture: all
Depends: ruby (>= 3.0), ruby-bundler, ruby-dev, build-essential
Maintainer: Tim Apple <tim.apple@hey.com>
Homepage: https://github.com/timappledotcom/siru
Description: A Hugo-inspired static site generator built in Ruby
 Siru is a fast, flexible static site generator inspired by Hugo, built in Ruby
 with support for themes, markdown processing, RSS feeds, and live reloading.
 .
 Features:
  - Markdown content rendering
  - Automatic RSS feed generation
  - SVG social media icons (Twitter, GitHub, Mastodon, Bluesky, Nostr)
  - Theme support with Liquid templating
  - Live server with file watching
  - TOML and YAML configuration support
  - Enhanced Paper theme with modern styling
